from Bug 367686 and Bug 367731 

uneval of sharp variables has issues..

few examples...

uneval of

 function(){
   return [#1=(3)]
 }

gives ==>

function () {
    return #1={}
}



uneval of 

function (){
  return [#1=({}) {__proto__: #1#}]
}


gives ==>

function () {
    return #1={ {__proto__:#1#}}
}




uneval of 

function (){
  return [#1=x {__proto__: #1#}]
}


gives ==>

function () {
    return #1={ {__proto__:#1#}}
}




But following unevals are fine

function (){
  return [1 #1=x {__proto__: #1#}]
}


and

function(){
   return [1 #1=(3)]
}

